#: ../../source/api/draw_of_lots.rst:2
msgid "Draw of Lots"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.draw_of_lots:1 of
msgid ""
"Terminal round resolved by lot when two contestants are tied across two "
"prior ballots."
msgstr ""
"Abschließende Runde, die per Los entschieden wird, wenn zwei Bewerber in "
"zwei vorangegangenen Wahlgängen gleichauf lagen."

#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots:1 of
msgid "A terminal election round decided by lot rather than by votes."
msgstr "Eine abschließende Wahlrunde, die per Los statt per Stimmenanzahl entschieden wird."

#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots:3 of
msgid ""
"Created when the same two contestants have faced each other in two "
"consecutive ballot rounds without either reaching the super-majority "
"threshold. No third ballot is cast — this draw-of-lots round is the third"
" round. The winner is determined by the configured "
":class:`~ipres.election_round.DrawLotsStrategy`."
msgstr ""
"Wird erzeugt, wenn dieselben zwei Bewerber in zwei aufeinanderfolgenden "
"Wahlgängen gegeneinander angetreten sind, ohne dass einer die "
"Supermehrheitsschwelle erreicht hat. Es gibt keinen dritten Wahlgang – "
"diese Losentscheid-Runde ist die dritte Runde. Der Sieger wird durch die "
"konfigurierte :class:`~ipres.election_round.DrawLotsStrategy` bestimmt."

#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots:9 of
msgid ""
"Vote data is delegated to the preceding :class:`~ipres.ballot.Ballot` "
"round via :meth:`getContestantsVotesAfterPossibleCoalitions`."
msgstr ""
"Stimmendaten werden über "
":meth:`getContestantsVotesAfterPossibleCoalitions` an den vorangehenden "
":class:`~ipres.ballot.Ballot`-Wahlgang delegiert."

#: ../../source/api/draw_of_lots.rst
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "Parameter"

#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots:15 of
msgid "The input that produced this draw."
msgstr "Der Input, der diesen Losentscheid erzeugt hat."

#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots of
msgid "type"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots:17 of
msgid "ipres.election_round.ElectionRoundInput"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots:21 of
msgid "The two contestants competing in this draw."
msgstr "Die zwei Bewerber, die an diesem Losentscheid teilnehmen."

#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots:23 of
msgid "dict[str, ipres.contestant.Contestant]"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots:27 of
msgid "The contestant selected by lot."
msgstr "Der per Los ausgewählte Bewerber."

#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots:29 of
msgid "ipres.contestant.Contestant"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots.getContestants:1 of
msgid "Return the two contestants that took part in this draw."
msgstr "Gibt die zwei Bewerber zurück, die an diesem Losentscheid teilgenommen haben."

#: ../../source/api/draw_of_lots.rst
#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots.getContestants
#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots.getDrawLotsStrategy
#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots.getElection
#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots.getNextRoundInput
#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots.getOriginalContestants
#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots.getParticipatingParties
#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots.getPreviousRound
#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots.getRoundNumber
#: ipres.draw_of_lots.DrawOfLots.getWinner
